The evidence with the title 'Donald Trump would 'bomb the shit out of ISIS' - Business Insider ' says Nov 13, 2015  ... During a speech at Decker Auditorium in Fort Dodge, Iowa, Trump said he would go after ISIS-controlled oil fields and "bomb the s--- out of 'em," to loud applause. "ISIS is making a tremendous amount of money because they have certain oil camps, certain areas of oil that they took away," Trump said. 
